Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.54,0:00:04.92,Song,,0,0,0,,Live, live on, with all your might
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.92,0:00:09.38,Song,,0,0,0,,Follow the light to the future
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.13,0:00:23.29,Song,,0,0,0,,Betrayed and left behind in this lonely world
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.63,0:00:28.83,Song,,0,0,0,,Fearing a tomorrow I've lost sight of
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.33,0:00:31.96,Song,,0,0,0,,I search for the place I belong
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.96,0:00:38.46,Song,,0,0,0,,My heart screams out, "I want to be needed"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.67,0:00:47.21,Song,,0,0,0,,I want to puzzle out these entwined identities, but can I trust them?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.21,0:00:50.58,Song,,0,0,0,,Live, live on, with all your might
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.58,0:00:54.58,Song,,0,0,0,,Follow the light to the future
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.92,0:00:58.08,Song,,0,0,0,,Even if you lose everything
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.08,0:01:02.46,Song,,0,0,0,,Stay connected to hope
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.67,0:01:06.17,Song,,0,0,0,,I don't know why I'm here
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.58,0:01:10.04,Song,,0,0,0,,But that's all right with me right now
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.42,0:01:13.92,Song,,0,0,0,,I have to overcome and press on
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.92,0:01:19.83,Song,,0,0,0,,So I can smile with you again
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.79,0:01:49.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,So, what's up, man?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.71,0:01:56.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,C'mon, tell me. You can tell your cool older bro about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.17,0:02:00.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Don't hold it in. Talk it out, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.58,0:02:06.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,My age.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.58,0:02:08.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Huh? What about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.25,0:02:14.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, Shutina mentioned\Nthat his birthday was not too long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.25,0:02:18.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What are you, sixteen? Seventeen?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.33,0:02:21.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Bet there aren't many people your age in the Army.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.08,0:02:23.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You sad about it, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.67,0:02:25.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Want us to throw you a big birthday party?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.00,0:02:27.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I want you to stop acting like you're older than me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.88,0:02:30.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,We're around the same age, aren't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.08,0:02:36.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,That's seriously the first thing you have to say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.75,0:02:45.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Sheesh, and I thought getting here was a pain…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.79,0:02:49.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.25,0:02:51.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'm going on a journey.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.58,0:02:53.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Please don't come looking for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.46,0:02:57.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I have failed to properly train my troops\Nand will be taking my life to make amends.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.17,0:02:58.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,The hell is this crap?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.67,0:03:00.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I-I mean, my word, what is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.58,0:03:02.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Mernes and Edvard…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.63,0:03:04.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,"Don't come looking for me"?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.67,0:03:06.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,"Taking my life to make amends?" Don't BS me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.71,0:03:10.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Why does every single one of\Nyou have the weirdest issues?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.67,0:03:12.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Where are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.21,0:03:16.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Edvard is at the training grounds,\Nbut we've no idea where Mernes is!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.29,0:03:19.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'll go after General Mernes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.63,0:03:22.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Thank you. I'll go seek out Edvard.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.75,0:03:23.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Shutina, Lily.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.92,0:03:24.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.00,0:03:28.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Echidna?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.04,0:03:28.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Your Highness!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.04,0:03:32.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You can barely walk! Please, let us go instead!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.42,0:03:34.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Fret not, I'll sober up right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.75,0:03:38.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Let us go!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.46,0:03:44.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'll reveal who I am once all of this is taken care of.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.29,0:03:52.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Good, there's still a faint trace of magic…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.71,0:03:55.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I thought Mernes and Edvard were managing just fine,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.79,0:03:58.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,but it sounds like they were\Nstruggling with things deep down…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.33,0:04:01.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Still, this is going overboard!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.25,0:04:04.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Do they only see things in black and white? Sheesh!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.67,0:04:06.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,He's close!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.88,0:04:11.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.54,0:04:15.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Hey! Hold up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.25,0:04:16.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It's me, Leo!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.25,0:04:30.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What was up with that letter?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.25,0:04:33.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You're 'going on a journey'?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.96,0:04:36.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You could've come up with something way better.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.58,0:04:41.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It's the truth. I just wanted to go on a little trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.08,0:04:44.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Great Generals can't just up\Nand vanish to 'go on a little trip'!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.21,0:04:49.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,If we lose even one of you now,\Nwe'll have to rebuild the army from scratch.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.13,0:04:55.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,So what's the deal? You want to quit,\Nor is something else bothering you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.21,0:04:56.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I don't care what it is, just spit it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.46,0:05:02.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,If Mernes tries to escape by running off,\NI might not be able to catch him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.29,0:05:04.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,And if he was serious about hiding from me,\NI probably wouldn't be able to find him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.92,0:05:08.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I can't let him get away from me\Nbefore I find out why he wants to leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.92,0:05:13.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,If you've really decided to leave,\Nthen I'm not going to stop you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.38,0:05:15.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Are you listening?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.63,0:05:19.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,There's nothing wrong with wanting to quit.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.75,0:05:22.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Hell, wanting to quit is a good sign\Nthat you should quit.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.63,0:05:27.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,If you've got a good reason, I'll go back to\Nthe castle and tell them I couldn't find you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.54,0:05:28.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,But…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.13,0:05:29.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,But what?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.00,0:05:36.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Look, when you want to quit a job,\Nyou want to make sure you're not going to regret it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.29,0:05:41.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Sure, you want to have your next job lined up,\Nget your replacement trained,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.13,0:05:43.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,and maybe punch your shithead boss in the face,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.88,0:05:48.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,but making sure you don't regret it is number one.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.46,0:05:54.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Other people might not want you to go,\Nbut if you want to go, that's all that matters.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.63,0:05:59.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,But if you've even the slightest doubt about it,\Nthen you should stop and take a breath.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.71,0:06:08.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,So, what's on your mind, Mernes?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.58,0:06:10.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You don't really want to leave the army, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.63,0:06:13.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.88,0:06:15.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It's just you and me here, so tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.83,0:06:18.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I won't laugh, I swear.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.79,0:06:19.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.83,0:06:26.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I know I'm right. C'mon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.83,0:06:29.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,This is gonna take a while…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.13,0:06:48.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Interviews.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.54,0:06:49.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.17,0:06:53.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,In three days, I'll have to conduct interviews by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.79,0:07:02.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,To do that, I need to be energetic\Nand imposing. Able to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.21,0:07:05.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'll be interviewing agents and spies.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.13,0:07:10.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,All people who have to be good at talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.96,0:07:13.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,And you're not a big talker.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.25,0:07:19.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,But weren't you a guild master before?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.25,0:07:22.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I let other people handle all the talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.29,0:07:24.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Same with the Demon Army, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.00,0:07:29.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,All right, all right. And I sent all those other\Npeople packing to the Demon World.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.58,0:07:37.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I thought I could learn something if\NI took a trip and visited lots of villages.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.54,0:07:40.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,But now that you're here, I don't need to.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.17,0:07:42.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,No more trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.33,0:07:44.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.67,0:07:51.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Leo, teach me how to hold conversations.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.50,0:07:54.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Turn me into a master communicator\Nin the next three days.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.00,0:07:56.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Uh, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.38,0:08:03.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Communication skills...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.00,0:08:09.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,One of the most important skills to have\Nwhen you're working with a team, that's for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.63,0:08:14.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,And you weren't sure how to train yourself\Nto be a good communicator, so here you are…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.08,0:08:17.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Wait, have you asked anyone for help yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.46,0:08:19.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'm asking now, aren't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.50,0:08:21.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I mean someone else!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.46,0:08:25.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I didn't know what to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.88,0:08:30.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,And everyone's so busy with their own work.\NI didn't want to bother them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.25,0:08:32.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,So you leave that cryptic letter instead?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.46,0:08:34.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Is your brain broken or something?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.21,0:08:38.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.13,0:08:47.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Fine. Three days, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.00,0:08:52.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,That was the extent of our conversation.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.13,0:08:57.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,For the time being, Mernes should\Nnot leave on any surprise journeys.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.71,0:08:59.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I see. Good work.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.71,0:09:00.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.96,0:09:02.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,We're in your debt, Lord Onyx.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.67,0:09:04.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Good job, L-
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.88,0:09:09.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I see now. I didn't know Mernes was so troubled…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.96,0:09:12.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Would you like to elaborate, Your Highness?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.58,0:09:17.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Oh, my apologies. The fact that Mernes\Nis troubled is extremely worrying.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.08,0:09:23.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,And yet despite that, he still tried\Nhis best to help the army rebuild…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.25,0:09:25.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.75,0:09:27.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Mernes is such a weirdo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.13,0:09:34.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You likely don't know this yet,\Nbut my Generals are also my consultants.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.00,0:09:39.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I listen to their thoughts, and Mernes' thoughts\Non humanity often clashed with mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.63,0:09:42.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I didn't know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.83,0:09:45.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I've lost. Kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.38,0:09:48.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,If you don't, then someday, I'll exterminate humanity.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.21,0:09:53.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I did realize he was a little off\Nbefore I came to the Demon Army.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.13,0:09:56.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,How did things fare with General Edvard?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.04,0:10:00.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Ah, yes. We rushed to the training grounds…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.63,0:10:07.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,That fool truly WAS trying to take his life...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.21,0:10:12.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,He should've known regular blades\Ncouldn't pierce his draconic scales!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.83,0:10:16.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Who knows what would've happened\Nif he'd tried poison instead…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.17,0:10:19.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,His stalwart dedication to warrior ideals saved his life.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.54,0:10:23.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,The reason he wrote in his letter was\Nhis failure to train his troops, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.33,0:10:29.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,He kept proclaiming he was 'a worthless general',\Nbut we haven't heard the full story yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.79,0:10:32.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Julietta is keeping an eye on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.25,0:10:37.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,His beloved daughter is his only weakness.\NWith her there, I have no worries.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.08,0:10:42.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,When he settles down, I hope\Nhe'll open up about his reasons...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.25,0:10:48.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Understood. When I've resolved Mernes' situation,\NI'll come assist you there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.79,0:10:50.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Onyx.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.13,0:11:16.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Sorry about the wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.63,0:11:19.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Here's the dwarven mushroom sautees for table 8!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.96,0:11:20.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.88,0:11:21.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.33,0:11:29.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much for waiting, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.83,0:11:30.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.92,0:11:34.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Thanks again! The food quality improvement\Nwas your doing too, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.88,0:11:36.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Now we're busier than ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.79,0:11:38.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'll teach 'em some more recipes later.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.63,0:11:41.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,The head cook's got a few tricks left up his sleeve!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.21,0:11:42.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Can't wait to taste it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.83,0:11:45.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,And now you've brought us little Mernie,\Nand she's so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.58,0:11:48.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Though with how quiet she is,\NI'd say the cat's got her tongue, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.58,0:11:49.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,See? You're cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.96,0:11:51.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,There's something wrong a--
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.21,0:11:53.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Here, one Goblin Salad for table 10!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.83,0:11:56.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Thanks! Can you take it out, Mernie?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.63,0:11:58.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.29,0:12:05.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I've got a Goblin Salad for you. Here you go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.67,0:12:06.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.17,0:12:09.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Leo.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.25,0:12:10.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.21,0:12:14.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I asked you to turn me into\Na master communicator, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.00,0:12:15.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You sure did.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.21,0:12:16.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,This is wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.38,0:12:19.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You want better people skills, yeah?\NWhat's wrong about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.46,0:12:23.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Why are we working in the mess hall?\NAnd why am I dressed like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.71,0:12:26.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You gotta see things from\Nyour underlings' point of view.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.58,0:12:30.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Think they could sit back and enjoy\Ntheir meals when their waiter is their General?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.75,0:12:32.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You needed a disguise!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.75,0:12:35.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Where's your disguise? You look just like the Hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.71,0:12:38.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,These guys won't remember what I looked like.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.88,0:12:41.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,But they know what YOU look like.\NEveryone'd recognize you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.88,0:12:43.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Why didn't I get the same uniform, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.71,0:12:46.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Because this was the only one in your size!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.75,0:12:48.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You're the dainty sort, anyway, so you look good in that!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.92,0:12:52.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,When do I get lessons on communication?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.71,0:12:58.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,We've been over this! Service positions teach\Nyou all the basics of communication!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.13,0:13:02.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Order up for Table 34, grilled rabbit!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.25,0:13:04.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Thanks! C'mon, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.88,0:13:05.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.42,0:13:20.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Mernie! You're gonna scare off our customers\Nwith that look! C'mon, big smile!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.92,0:13:26.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,That's even scarier. Come now, you're not an assassin!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.50,0:13:31.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Facial expression is part of being a good server.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.54,0:13:36.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Why bother teaching me all the basics?\NI don't have the talent for communication.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.75,0:13:38.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Just keep that in mind, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.71,0:13:42.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Don't get all smug on me.\NAnd communication isn't about talent.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.96,0:13:45.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I was terrible at it back in the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.63,0:13:48.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I was constantly embarrassing myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.25,0:13:50.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yeah, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.71,0:13:52.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.50,0:13:57.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You have no idea how many people I've talked to,\Nor how many times I've failed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.29,0:14:02.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,But that's just what communication is:\Npractice and experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.67,0:14:08.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,And the mess hall's the best place in the castle\Nfor you to get that experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.25,0:14:10.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.38,0:14:10.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.63,0:14:15.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You should start by not responding\Nwith 'whatever' all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.96,0:14:20.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Order up for Table 2, twelve noodle soups!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.46,0:14:22.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Remember this, Mernie.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.92,0:14:25.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Conversation is a group effort.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.96,0:14:30.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,They throw you some words, you catch them,\Nthen throw some back. That's the key.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.08,0:14:33.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,That's vague. Be more specific.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.00,0:14:37.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You want them to know you're listening to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.38,0:14:40.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Imagine yourself in their shoes and hear them out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.54,0:14:46.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,For example, if you were eating\Nthese noodles with someone…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.46,0:14:47.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.25,0:14:49.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Y-yes, they are!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.13,0:14:50.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.88,0:14:55.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,There are an infinite number of replies\Nto the statement "this is delicious".
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.00,0:14:57.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You could agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.08,0:14:59.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Indeed, indeed!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.08,0:15:02.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You could emphatically disagree.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.88,0:15:05.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'm not a fan of them, either...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.42,0:15:08.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You could say you'd rather have steak instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.50,0:15:10.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I wanna eat meat, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.83,0:15:16.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,The right way to answer is to piece\Ntogether how the other person feels.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.17,0:15:21.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What are they trying to say?\NWhat emotion are they expressing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.67,0:15:26.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,And whether it's a work conversation\Nor friendly chitchat, empathy is key.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.67,0:15:31.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,See it from their point of view,\Nfigure out what they want to talk about.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.63,0:15:36.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Empathy is the first thing they tell you to get rid\Nof when you join the Assassin's Guild.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.00,0:15:38.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Assassin's Guild…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.50,0:15:41.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Aren't there any secret communication\Ntechniques you could teach me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.54,0:15:45.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Secret techniques? Let's see…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.17,0:15:53.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I suppose it's not reasonable to expect\Nan assassin trained from birth to have empathy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.92,0:16:00.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Sure. Secret technique number one:\NShut up and listen. That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.58,0:16:01.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yeah, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.04,0:16:04.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Ow! The hell was that for?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.46,0:16:06.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What kind of conversation would that be, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.58,0:16:08.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'm being serious here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.38,0:16:11.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You know how the saying goes,\Na good communicator is a good listener!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.00,0:16:13.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I already stay quiet all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.88,0:16:16.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Because you just want the conversation to be over!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.58,0:16:24.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Like I said before, conversation is a group activity.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.46,0:16:27.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Listening intently to what the other person\Nis saying is how you have a good conversation.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.04,0:16:31.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,That's what I did the first time\NI tried to have a human conversation.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.38,0:16:34.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,A human conversation…?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.75,0:16:36.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It'll make sense soon enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.67,0:16:39.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Once people know you're a good listener,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.25,0:16:43.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,they'll start coming to you,\Nasking to vent or to get some advice.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.46,0:16:44.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.67,0:16:48.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Really. It feels good to get stuff off their chest.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.96,0:16:51.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Complaints about work, relationships,\Nanything on their mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.46,0:16:54.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You're gonna be interviewing people, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.75,0:16:57.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Then you should focus on listening instead of talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.71,0:17:00.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It'll all work out, I promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.29,0:17:05.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,See their point of view and listen...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.42,0:17:07.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Hey, waitress! Can I order?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.21,0:17:09.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yes, coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.33,0:17:12.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Apologies for the wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.33,0:17:15.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You sure took your damn time!\NWe've been callin' for ya this whole time!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.75,0:17:20.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,We're the Howlers of the Moonlit Night!\NYou don't wanna get on our shit list!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.58,0:17:22.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Oh, the new mercenaries.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.04,0:17:27.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Edvard is supposed to make sure they stay in line,\Nbut yeah, he's not doing that right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.38,0:17:33.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Whoa, whoa, our slowpoke waitress is a hell of a cutie!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.38,0:17:34.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What would you like to order?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.54,0:17:37.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Beer, and meat! On the double, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.08,0:17:42.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'll need more information that that.\NWe have a variety of ales and meats.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.58,0:17:47.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Aww, they have a variety of ales and meats!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.38,0:17:57.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,We have a vawiety of ales and meats! A vawiety!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.33,0:17:58.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What a cutie!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.33,0:18:05.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Might I suggest the meat-stuffed red pepper?\NIt paires quite nicely with ale...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.33,0:18:08.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'm more hungry for a pretty woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.04,0:18:14.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What you doin' tonight, sweetheart?\NI'll show you a good time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.04,0:18:18.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,That is not a service we provide here in the mess hall.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.58,0:18:24.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Don't be like that! I've made succubi cry\Nout in pleasure before, y'know!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.54,0:18:32.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What are you standing around and doing nothing for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.00,0:18:33.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,If you won't do something, then I will!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.71,0:18:35.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,She's fine. Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.58,0:18:36.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.00,0:18:41.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Touch me again and I break your arm.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.50,0:18:44.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You broke it, you broke it, you already broke it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.50,0:18:48.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I haven't broken it yet. If I bend it\Na little more, though, I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.92,0:18:48.46,Subtitle-2,,0,0,0,,Ow, ow, ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.17,0:18:50.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.29,0:18:52.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,The hell did you do to the boss?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.88,0:19:14.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.04,0:19:19.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Are you done? I can take you all if you want to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.71,0:19:23.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Are you done?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.08,0:19:25.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,We're done!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.42,0:19:26.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,We're so sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.46,0:19:28.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Wait, is that General Mernes?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.88,0:19:31.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,No, what would he be doing down here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.17,0:19:32.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Did you see that just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.71,0:19:35.67,Subtitle-3,,0,0,0,,I can't believe it, she's as tough as General Mernes!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.08,0:19:37.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Might want to teach him how to disguise himself better.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.38,0:19:43.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'm tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.83,0:19:47.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Good job today. Not bad for your first day of work.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.21,0:19:49.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You kicked ass, and not just those werewolves'.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.63,0:19:51.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,All I did was hurt them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.42,0:19:53.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,That's how you deal with chumps like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.96,0:19:58.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,But you also gave them a suggestion\Nfor what to order, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.83,0:20:00.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Did I do an alright job?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.92,0:20:04.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that was great. You did way better than I expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.33,0:20:06.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.42,0:20:07.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I shouldn't be surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.17,0:20:13.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Just like Lily's leadership skills, he had the basics down,\Nbut never had the opportunity to hone his skills.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.00,0:20:15.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Nothing more than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.58,0:20:18.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,So, now what?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.58,0:20:19.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,We'll wrap up what we learned today.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.17,0:20:22.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Get changed and meet me in my room.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.42,0:20:29.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Cool, sit over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.33,0:20:31.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What're we doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.54,0:20:37.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Practice makes perfect, so I'm going\Nto do a practice interview with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.00,0:20:41.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,So I'm going to interview you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.71,0:20:47.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yep. You learned a bunch today,\Nso your skills are already on the up and up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.08,0:20:51.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Pretend this is a real interview and\Nstart by asking me anything you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.67,0:20:54.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.13,0:20:58.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yeah, anything. Just use what I taught you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.71,0:21:02.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Okay, what's he gonna ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.58,0:21:05.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Something about my infiltration or spy skills,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.17,0:21:08.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,or maybe the reason I want to join up with the army?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.88,0:21:15.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,See it from their point of view,\Nfigure out what they want to talk about.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.00,0:21:17.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Once people know you're a good listener,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.50,0:21:20.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,they'll start coming to you,\Nasking to vent or to get some advice.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.25,0:21:24.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You'll answer whatever question I ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.04,0:21:27.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yeah, and honestly, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.21,0:21:32.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Wait, what was that look for?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.67,0:21:35.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,That's the kind of look an assassin gives you\Nwhen he's found your weakness.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.92,0:21:38.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Oh, boy. I have a bad feeling about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.58,0:21:40.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'm going to regret saying that, aren't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.92,0:21:43.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Then I want to know your reason for joining us.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.63,0:21:47.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Guess I shouldn't have worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.67,0:21:53.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,So…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.92,0:21:54.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.38,0:21:59.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You said you wanted to join us\Nto bring ruin to humanity.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.25,0:22:01.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,But that's a lie, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.17,0:22:23.42,Song,,0,0,0,,Our hearts are always so frail and fragile
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.42,0:22:29.58,Song,,0,0,0,,But we still face forward and continue down our long road
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.67,0:22:35.25,Song,,0,0,0,,If we don't know something now, we can go learn about it
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.54,0:22:42.17,Song,,0,0,0,,We might not know what's at the end of our long, continuing journey
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.38,0:22:48.21,Song,,0,0,0,,Don't try to do everything yourself, lean on us sometimes
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.46,0:22:51.96,Song,,0,0,0,,Sharing your weaknesses is strength in itself
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.96,0:22:56.38,Song,,0,0,0,,There's still a long way to go,\Nso make sure you won't regret anything
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.88,0:22:59.79,Song,,0,0,0,,Dash on! The reason's simple
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.79,0:23:03.25,Song,,0,0,0,,Let loose! Make your dreams reality
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.25,0:23:09.38,Song,,0,0,0,,The future you're heading towards is one you shape yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.38,0:23:15.04,Song,,0,0,0,,It's okay to be scared of change, you can go little by little
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.04,0:23:19.25,Song,,0,0,0,,I want to protect the things I cherish
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.25,0:23:21.83,Song,,0,0,0,,(I'm so glad we found each other)
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.83,0:23:26.17,Song,,0,0,0,,So I hope you hear how thankful I am for you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.04,0:01:36.79,Caption,,0,0,0,,{\pos(691.2,612)}{\an7}If You Want to Quit, Talk It Out First
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.83,0:23:40.42,Caption-2,,0,0,0,,{\pos(998.4,100.8)}{\an7}Next Time:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.83,0:23:40.42,Caption-2,,0,0,0,,{\pos(179.2,187.2)}{\an7}The Hero
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.84,0:23:40.42,Caption-2,,0,0,0,,{\pos(204.8,244.8)}{\an7}Shares
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.84,0:23:40.42,Caption-2,,0,0,0,,{\pos(896,295.2)}{\an7}His Tale
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.84,0:23:40.42,Caption-2,,0,0,0,,{\pos(883.2,352.8)}{\an7}of Burden
